{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775824134477,"sessionID":"ses_288a58108ffeS1DUsDMwJC33nz","part":{"id":"prt_d775de14a001IT7O5ko4GiJk7f","messageID":"msg_d775dd35b0015fD1kkVcryQAnG","sessionID":"ses_288a58108ffeS1DUsDMwJC33nz","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775824136496,"sessionID":"ses_288a58108ffeS1DUsDMwJC33nz","part":{"id":"prt_d775de4a90016E4ycGCfuZDSZO","messageID":"msg_d775dd35b0015fD1kkVcryQAnG","sessionID":"ses_288a58108ffeS1DUsDMwJC33nz","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_63e4b4ede58047b5a7419cac","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-3 (Design Complete)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: L\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 reconciler 包与内部类型定义\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/` 目录\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 创建 `types.go`，定义 `resourceType` 常量：`resourceTypeAgentRuntime = \"agentruntime\"`、`resourceTypeCodeInterpreter = \"codeinterpreter\"`、`resourceTypePod = \"pod\"`\n14: - [ ] T-001.03 定义结果常量：`resultSuccess = \"success\"`、`resultError = \"error\"`\n15: - [ ] T-001.04 定义错误类型常量：`errorTypeStoreUnreachable = \"store_unreachable\"`、`errorTypeListerFailure = \"lister_failure\"`、`errorTypeInvalidData = \"invalid_data\"`、`errorTypeUpdateFailed = \"update_failed\"`\n16: - [ ] T-001.05 定义条件常量：`ConditionReady = \"Ready\"`、`ReasonTerminated = \"Terminated\"`\n17: - [ ] T-001.06 定义运行时常量：`maxRetries = 15`、`defaultWorkers = 2`、`cacheSyncTimeout = 30 * time.Second`、`shutdownTimeout = 30 * time.Second`\n18: - [ ] T-001.07 定义 `ReconcilerDeps` 结构体，字段：`Clientset clientset.Interface`、`InformerFactory externalversions.SharedInformerFactory`、`ARLister listers.AgentRuntimeLister`、`CILister listers.CodeInterpreterLister`、`PodInformer coreinformers.PodInformer`、`Store Store`、`Workers int`、`MetricsRecorder MetricsRecorder`\n19: - [ ] T-001.08 定义 `Store` 接口（若 handler 层尚未导出，则在本包定义）：`StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info) error`、`UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info) error`、`DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) error`、`GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID) (*SandboxInfo, error)`、`ListSandboxes(ctx) (map[string]*SandboxInfo, error)`\n20: \n21: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过；所有常量值与设计文档一致；`ReconcilerDeps` 字段类型正确\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## T-002: 实现 MetricsRecorder 接口与 Prometheus 实现\n26: \n27: - [ ] T-002.01 在 `types.go` 中定义 `MetricsRecorder` 接口：`IncReconcileTotal(resourceType, result string)`、`ObserveReconcileDuration(resourceType string, duration time.Duration)`、`IncReconcileErrors(resourceType, errorType string)`、`SetWorkqueueDepth(depth int)`、`IncWorkqueueAdds(resourceType string)`\n28: - [ ] T-002.02 创建 `metrics.go`，定义 `PrometheusMetricsRecorder` 结构体，字段：`reconcileTotal *prometheus.CounterVec`、`reconcileDuration *prometheus.HistogramVec`、`reconcileErrors *prometheus.CounterVec`、`workqueueDepth prometheus.Gauge`、`workqueueAdds *prometheus.CounterVec`\n29: - [ ] T-002.03 实现 `NewPrometheusMetricsRecorder(reg prometheus.Registerer) *PrometheusMetricsRecorder` 构造函数\n30: - [ ] T-002.04 实现 `reconcile_total` Counter，labels：`resource_type`、`result`\n31: - [ ] T-002.05 实现 `reconcile_duration_seconds` Histogram，buckets：`[0.01, 0.05, 0.1, 0.5, 1, 5, 10, 30]`\n32: - [ ] T-002.06 实现 `reconcile_errors_total` Counter，labels：`resource_type`、`error_type`\n33: - [ ] T-002.07 实现 `workqueue_depth` Gauge\n34: - [ ] T-002.08 实现 `workqueue_adds_total` Counter，label：`resource_type`\n35: - [ ] T-002.09 所有接口方法在 receiver 为 nil 时 no-op（nil-safe）\n36: \n37: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过；`NewPrometheusMetricsRecorder` 返回非 nil 实例；nil receiver 调用所有方法不 panic；Prometheus 指标名称/labels/buckets 与设计文档一致\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## T-003: 编写 MetricsRecorder 单元测试\n42: \n43: - [ ] T-003.01 创建 `metrics_test.go`\n44: - [ ] T-003.02 测试 `TestNewPrometheusMetricsRecorder`：返回非 nil 实例，指标已注册\n45: - [ ] T-003.03 测试 `TestPrometheusMetricsRecorder_IncReconcileTotal`：调用后 counter 值 +1\n46: - [ ] T-003.04 测试 `TestPrometheusMetricsRecorder_ObserveReconcileDuration`：调用后 histogram 记录值\n47: - [ ] T-003.05 测试 `TestPrometheusMetricsRecorder_IncReconcileErrors`：调用后 error counter +1\n48: - [ ] T-003.06 测试 `TestPrometheusMetricsRecorder_SetWorkqueueDepth`：调用后 gauge 值更新\n49: - [ ] T-003.07 测试 `TestPrometheusMetricsRecorder_IncWorkqueueAdds`：调用后 adds counter +1\n50: - [ ] T-003.08 测试 `TestMetricsRecorder_NilReceiver`：nil receiver 调用所有方法不 panic\n51: - [ ] T-003.09 测试 `TestMetricsRecorder_NilInterface`：`MetricsRecorder` 接口变量为 nil 时调用不 panic\n52: \n53: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/... -run TestMetrics -v` 全部通过；nil 安全路径全覆盖\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## T-004: 实现 SandboxReconciler 结构体与构造函数\n58: \n59: - [ ] T-004.01 创建 `reconciler.go`\n60: - [ ] T-004.02 定义 `SandboxReconciler` 结构体，字段：`clientset clientset.Interface`、`arLister listers.AgentRuntimeLister`、`ciLister listers.CodeInterpreterLister`、`store Store`、`workqueue workqueue.RateLimitingInterface`、`workers int`、`metricsRecorder MetricsRecorder`、`mu sync.Mutex`、`running bool`、`stopCh chan struct{}`\n61: - [ ] T-004.03 实现 `NewSandboxReconciler(deps ReconcilerDeps) *SandboxReconciler` 构造函数\n62: - [ ] T-004.04 构造函数验证必需依赖：`deps.Store` 非 nil、`deps.Clientset` 非 nil、`deps.InformerFactory` 非 nil，否则 panic（或返回 error，按项目约定）\n63: - [ ] T-004.05 构造函数初始化 workqueue：`workqueue.NewNamedRateLimitingQueue(workqueue.NewItemExponentialFailureRateLimiter(5*time.Second, 5*time.Minute), \"sandbox-reconciler\")`\n64: - [ ] T-004.06 构造函数处理 `deps.Workers == 0` 时默认为 `defaultWorkers`（2）\n65: - [ ] T-004.07 构造函数处理 `deps.MetricsRecorder == nil` 时不 panic，字段保持 nil\n66: \n67: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过；构造函数返回非 nil `*SandboxReconciler`；workqueue 已初始化且速率限制策略正确；可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## T-005: 编写构造函数与结构体单元测试\n72: \n73: - [ ] T-005.01 创建 `reconciler_test.go`\n74: - [ ] T-005.02 测试 `TestNewSandboxReconciler_AllDeps`：所有依赖提供时返回非 nil Reconciler，所有字段正确赋值\n75: - [ ] T-005.03 测试 `TestNewSandboxReco