\n- [ ] T-026.06 新增 `TestSandboxListItem_IsIdle_Populated`：列表项中 IsIdle 字段正确填充\n\n**验收**: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handler/... -run TestCalculateTimeToIdle -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T-027: 全量验证门禁\n\n- [ ] T-027.01 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] T-027.02 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n- [ ] T-027.03 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out` 行覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] T-027.04 T/C 比率 > 0.4（测试代码行数 / 源代码行数）\n- [ ] T-027.05 `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 无 data race 告警\n- [ ] T-027.06 `grep -n 'log\\.Printf' handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` 无匹配结果\n- [ ] T-027.07 GC 清理原因常量验证：ttl_expired / idle / orphan_cr / ghost_entry 均被正确使用\n- [ ] T-027.08 闲置超时清理验证：LastActivityAt + idleTimeout < now 时沙箱被清理\n- [ ] T-027.09 孤儿 CR 清理验证：Store 中无对应条目的 CR 被删除，数量受 MaxOrphanScanLimit 限制\n- [ ] T-027.10 幽灵条目清理验证：K8s 中 CR 已不存在的 Store 条目被清理\n- [ ] T-027.11 GC 指标验证：gc_cleanup_total、gc_cleanup_duration_seconds、gc_cleanup_errors_total、gc_cycle_duration_seconds 均正确记录\n- [ ] T-027.12 结构化日志验证：所有 GC 日志使用 slog，包含 session_id/sandbox_name/namespace/reason 字段\n- [ ] T-027.13 LastActivityAt 验证：创建/更新/访问时均被刷新\n- [ ] T-027.14 响应字段验证：SandboxStatusResponse 和 SandboxListItem 包含 LastActivityAt/TimeToIdle/IsIdle\n- [ ] T-027.15 GC 循环幂等性验证：Start → Stop → Start → Stop 无 panic，无 goroutine 泄漏\n- [ ] T-027.16 现有测试不被破坏：`sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` 中已有测试全部通过\n\n**验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-008 可标记为完成\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-008/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime.go\">\nERROR [51:25] undefined: LabelSessionID\nERROR [77:29] undefined: LabelSandboxName\nERROR [78:29] undefined: LabelWorkloadName\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/wor